{"id": 1452, "genre": 1000, "title": "你会因为“来都来了”的心理而干出哪些事儿？", "description": "因为舍不得 6 折打车券，我在雾霾指数 280 的天气去国贸溜达了一圈。（题图来自：Nadav Weisman）", "record_count": 19341, "comment_count": 29, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170115232146Du8XotiCApGq6OeB.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-01-18T17:00:11Z", "questions": [{"id": 1718, "title": "你会因为“来都来了”的心理而干出哪些事儿？", "content": "你会因为“舍不得”而干出那些事儿？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 154202, "content": "来都来了，去旅游景点看看", "image": "img/option/option/20170115225449HrQ4E6nwe25ahjD8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 154203, "content": "别浪费，食物再难吃也要吃完", "image": "img/option/option/201701152256104t6uolYZyWv8eIKT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 154204, "content": "贵衣服，即使丑也要拿出来穿", "image": "img/option/option/20170115230142tER2vYmcVNr36Bh7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 154205, "content": "谈了好几年感觉可惜，拖着不分手", "image": "img/option/option/20170115230906ZWLRTYtrBV1q3d8C.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 154206, "content": "开始看了，即使电影/书再烂也要看完", "image": "img/option/option/20170115231146w6jOKWZpI2Y5fUsl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 154216, "content": "网购时多买点东西凑满减", "image": "img/option/option/20170115231550LG7Fkemx5JZoyUN6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 154248, "content": "报名费都交了，不如去考考看", "image": "img/option/option/20170115231815CNVvbKpyDsdruaQ4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}